name: Rebel Hood
description: REBEL is not just another cryptocurrency, it's a movement born from the frustrations of countless traders who have been exploited by bad actors in the crypto space. Fueled by these experiences, REBEL is committed to creating a community-driven ecosystem that prioritizes fairness, transparency, and decentralization. With a Community-First Philosophy, REBEL goes beyond traditional tokenomics. The community directly influences the development and evolution of the project, ensuring that every decision aligns with the needs of the people it serves.
